data.meta_description: Leandro Gaudiano profile player page. Goals, matches, stats, player ratings and more.
data.text:
Leandro Gaudiano is 23 years old (Nov 21, 2000), 177 cm tall and plays for SV Muttenz.

If Leandro Gaudiano is going to be in SV Muttenz lineup, it will be confirmed on Sofascore one hour before the match starts.

If Leandro Gaudiano plays you will also be able to follow his live Sofascore rating, statistics and heatmap. Leandro Gaudiano football player profile displays all matches and competitions with statistics for all the matches Leandro Gaudiano played in. Most important stats for each competition, including average Sofascore rating, matches played, goals, assists, cards and other relevant data are also displayed.
